            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Crea una condición que ejecute el código si <code>replay_times</code> es mayor o igual a <code>300</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"song = \" /><text value=\"&quot;Don't stop me now&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"replay_times = \" /><text value=\"345\" class=\"number\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"if\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" replay_times &gt;= \" /><text value=\"300\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Your top song this week: &quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  print(song)\" /><text type=\"break\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"50\" endIndex=\"62\" /><option startIndex=\"63\" endIndex=\"65\" /><option startIndex=\"66\" endIndex=\"69\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Your top song this week: \" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Don't stop me now\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>replay_times</code> seguido de <code>&gt;=</code> y finalmente <code>300</code>.</p></body></html>"
