            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Usa <code>&gt;=</code> para escribir una condición que verifique si la <code>age</code> del usuario es mayor o igual a <code>18</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"age = \" /><text value=\"20\" class=\"number\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"can_drive = \" /><text value=\"False\" class=\"literal\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"if\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" age &gt;= \" /><text value=\"18\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\": \" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  can_drive = \" /><text value=\"True\" class=\"literal\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"print(can_drive)\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"31\" endIndex=\"34\" /><option startIndex=\"35\" endIndex=\"37\" /><option startIndex=\"38\" endIndex=\"40\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"True\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>age</code> seguido de <code>&gt;=</code> y finalmente <code>18</code>.</p></body></html>"
